President Obama announced his intent to nominate several individuals to key Administration posts. Eric K. Fanning was nominated for Under Secretary of the Air Force, Department of Defense. Christopher J. Meade was nominated for General Counsel, Department of the Treasury. William J. Mielke was nominated for Member, Advisory Board of the Saint Lawrence Seaway Development Corporation. Captain Arthur H. Sulzer, USN (ret) was nominated for Member, Advisory Board of the Saint Lawrence Seaway Development Corporation. Iqbal Paroo was nominated for Member, Board of Directors of the African Development Foundation. Hill Harper was appointed as a Member of the President's Cancer Panel. President Obama expressed confidence in the abilities of these individuals and looks forward to working with them in the future.